thread.title: Lesley Cains
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Lesley Cains

author: Lesley Cains
title: Lesley Cains
text:
I prefer to purchase my ink cartridges from Ink Station, as the price is very competitive, especially with the free delivery as I live quite remotely.
My personal preference is to buy the original Canon ink cartridges, and I appreciate the specials Ink Station has.
Delivery is fast, and the product packed well so it's never been damaged in transit to date.
